                        habt von Juda des juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        von <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        die also <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey uns zerten, vil und
                                <expan>mang<ex>er</ex>ley</expan>
<expan>anfechtigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>; wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu lieb <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        im <expan>gönne<ex>n</ex></expan> vier <expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>nehste<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns zu zern
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>, sein schulde bey uns
                                <expan>einczubringe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
